    <p>
        <a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=G_clJP1VGtk">GCSE Biology Revision "The Eye"</a>
    </p>
    <p>
        - The eye is a sense organ containing receptors sensitive to light intensity and colour.
    </p>
